											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="Kathoom! An arcane explosion! A chunk of crystaline enegy from the globe breaks of in a collision course for the player.&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;|In the background the dark figures unleash a barrage of lightning at the shield. It seems to break. The lightning splits and strikes some of the angel creatures. The tide of battle is turning. Daisy's attention is pulled away to this while they speak.|" />
										</node>
