											<attribute id="key" type="FixedString" value="CinematicNodeContext" />
											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="Whisps of magic waft toward the player's face, calming their tadpole and the pain they feel. Their eyes open to see Daisy - in armour, powerful, angelic, battle-weary, casting some spell on the player's head&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;Daisy kneels down by our side, left foot forward, lift up a hand and cast healing spell. Player sits up in a start.&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;They are confused - are they hallucinating? We see their skin showing signs of illithid transformation." />
