											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="[LILI] Angelic creature and dark figure fighting., Angelic creature strenghtening barrier defending against dark figure., Dark figure casting lignthing spell, trying to break barrier" />
										</node>
										<node id="data">
											<attribute id="key" type="FixedString" value="Attitude" />
											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="Default" />
										</node>
										<node id="data">
											<attribute id="key" type="FixedString" value="CinematicNodeContext" />
											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="Lighting cracks, it's close, the player's attention is pulled to a giant space skull with a globe of crystaline-like energy forming around it--like a bubble freezing in the winter.&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;A strange zolly move almost drags Daisy and the player's astal island closer to the skull: https://youtu.be/fP6QrESd7Fs&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;|The background changes. Plants wilt, the sky gets gets darker. We see glimpses of battle in the distance between angelic wisps and dark, armoured figures. The origin of the sounds we heard before become clear. It is lightning being thrown at the angelic creatures. The lightning deflects on them. They are casting a spell that is creating a magical globe around someone. The globe is not fully formed yet.|" />
										</node>
